                <note rend="inline" type="source">835.73/107a: Telegram</note>
                <head>
                    <hi rend="italic">The <gloss type="from">Secretary of State</gloss> to the
                        Ambassador in Argentina</hi> (<persName type="to">
                        <hi rend="italic">Stimson</hi>
                    </persName>)</head>
                <opener>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">
                        <placeName>
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">Washington</hi>
                        </placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1919-12-15T16:00:00-05:00">
                            <hi rend="italic">December 15, 1919, 4 p.m.</hi>
                        </date>
                    </dateline>
                </opener>
                <p>Consult Stabler concerning his telegram December 4 to Merrill. Advise Department
                    result of your conference with Minister for Foreign Affairs mentioned therein.
                    Why is signing of decree still delayed?</p>
                <closer>
                    <signed>
                        <hi rend="smallcaps">Lansing</hi>
                    </signed>
                </closer>
            </div>
        </body>
    </text>
